# Codic standard library — chords
#
# Chord shapes understood by .chord(root, name):
#   major     0 4 7
#   minor     0 3 7
#   dom7      0 4 7 10
#   maj7      0 4 7 11
#   min7      0 3 7 10
#   dim       0 3 6
#   aug       0 4 8
#   sus2      0 2 7
#   sus4      0 5 7
#
# Example:
#   chord("c", "min7").out()
